{"tid":1458240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"即刻開始向你身邊所有人 宣傳8月18號呢一日","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:29:49.000Z","uid":162060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2b4a618b80f02b858e7023ac3514f75d81b9c5","tid":1458240,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6FErc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6FErc1.jpg&h=5c287bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">616</span>&mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\">818</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔理你喺邊個，<br />\n<br />\n即刻約定曬你身邊所有人<span style=\"color: red;\">8月18號</span>！<br />\n<br />\n宣傳得有咁多得咁多！<span style=\"color: violet;\">時間好寶貴！</span><br />\n<br />\n同所有人講！屋企人、朋友、同事、同學、網友、外國人、街上面既人⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n今次唔係捍衛民主咁簡單，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今次喺捍衛人權！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人同你講佢驚，驚有黑社會同臥底而唔出黎行。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你同佢講：你今次唔出，唔好旨意你以後有得安全出去行街。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宜家！即刻！<br />\n開！始！宣！傳！</span></span>"},{"pid":"266a8f9b1d05df44607d431bf7e4da43bf0aa931","tid":1458240,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">616</span> &mdash; <span style=\"color: red;\">818</span></span>"},{"pid":"800b7a75f8cb51078061e133b2eacfc16f530cf1","tid":1458240,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">616</span> &mdash; <span style=\"color: red;\">818</span></span>"},{"pid":"7281d24b0a0caa85b19de15ab6b7f0f459851d6c","tid":1458240,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"h